	"keywords": "Career, Career Development, Career Advice, Software Development",
	"description": "Over the past five years, I&#x27;ve given dozens of guest lectures at many of the\ncoding bootcamps in Chicago. \n\nA few questions never fail to come up: &quot;Which language should I learn next?\n[/news/what-programming-language-should-i-learn-first-19a33b0a467d/]&quot;, &quot;How can\nI prepare for technical interviews? [/news/interviewing-prep-tips-and-tricks/]&quot;,\n&quot;Are you hiring?&quot;\n\nBut one question that threw me off was, &quot;What if I don&#x27;t want to be a software\ndeveloper?&quot;\n\nI&#x27;ve been thinking about this a lot lately. ",
